          "email_subject": "[REVIEW & SEND] Follow-up draft for Kris \u2014 Quick SiteZeus Sync",
          "email_html": "<p>Hi Kris,</p>\n<p>Thank you for taking the time to connect with me today. I wanted to follow up with a quick recap of what we covered.</p>\n<p><strong>What we discussed:</strong></p>\n<p>Will from SiteZeus, along with CFE from Batteries Plus, discussed the delivery of a presentation deck and the value of SiteZeus's new initiative for franchise development and sales. CFE plans to present the initiative as a fait accompli to his team, highlighting its benefits for territory creation and franchisee upsells, and requested a list of SiteZeus's major clients for peer validation. They also confirmed a split payment arrangement for billing and agreed to await legal review before proceeding with the contract.</p>\n<p><strong>Next steps:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>I've got a quick I'll send over a loom that walks through the new presentation templates as well if you'd like to show it.</li><li>So if there's interest there, I'll share that.</li><li>I'll send that right now.</li><li>I'm going to send it off to legal this week.</li><li>We'll take that split payment that'll get Peter a little bit less angst in his life around capital.</li></ul>\n<p><strong>Resources:</strong></p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/products/customer-insights-platform\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">Customer Insights</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/products/site-selection-software\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">SiteZeus Locate</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/products/construction-management-software\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">SiteZeus Build</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/products/franchise-crm\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">SiteZeus Sell</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/customer-stories\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">Customer Stories</a></li></ul>\n<p>Best,<br>wmorgan@sitezeus.com</p>",
          "status": "dashboard",
          "timestamp": "2026-06-08T17:56:35.490329+00:00"
        },
        {
