          "email_subject": "[REVIEW & SEND] Follow-up draft for Dave \u2014 SiteZeus <> Victory Lane Proposal",
          "email_html": "<p>Hi Dave,</p>\n<p>Thank you for taking the time to connect with me today. I wanted to follow up with a quick recap of what we covered.</p>\n<p><strong>What we discussed:</strong></p>\n<p>Mitch and Ian from SiteZeus, along with David from Victory Lane Quick Oil Change Inc., discussed SiteZeus's platform for customer insights, competitor benchmarking, and site selection, which David believes could have positively influenced two of his company's recent location decisions. David expressed significant interest but needs to discuss affordability with his team, and they agreed to follow up by the end of the following week. The SiteZeus team confirmed full implementation and support, with onboarding taking four to six weeks.</p>\n<p><strong>Next steps:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>I will, I will take whatever we talk about and I'll catch you guys up on Monday and then we'll go from there.</li><li>But what I will do is I'll have this discussion with the folks on Monday and I actually take that back.</li><li>But we will have the discussion and I'll give you feedback one way or the other.</li><li>I'm going to get ready for one more, I have before I can go home for the weekend here.</li><li>But, are you going to send this to me so I can show it to him?</li></ul>\n<p><strong>Resources:</strong></p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/products/site-selection-software\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">SiteZeus Locate</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/products/construction-management-software\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">SiteZeus Build</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/products/franchise-crm\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">SiteZeus Sell</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/products/customer-insights-platform\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">Customer Insights</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/customer-stories\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">Customer Stories</a></li></ul>\n<p>Best,<br>Mitchell Gunderson</p>",
