          "email_subject": "[REVIEW & SEND] Follow-up draft for Brad \u2014 SiteZeus <> Neighborly Meeting",
          "email_html": "<p>Hi Brad,</p>\n<p>Thank you for taking the time to connect with me today. I wanted to follow up with a quick recap of what we covered.</p>\n<p><strong>What we discussed:</strong></p>\n<p>Sean, Ian and Lucas from SiteZeus, along with Neighborly Brands team members, discussed the analysis of Mr. Rooter's territory performance, identifying key demographic drivers for revenue and highlighting discrepancies in current data reporting that necessitate further investigation and refinement of the territory modeling. The team aims to develop a more accurate territory formula by addressing data quality issues and outlier performance to optimize future franchise growth.</p>\n<p><strong>Next steps:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>I'll double check it's.</li><li>So we'll just give him a minute or two.</li><li>We're doing essentially a second analysis that we'll be presenting today.</li><li>So today we'll be walking through the portfolio driven territory formula for mr reuter as well as spending some time hopping back in.</li><li>I'm going to hand it over to Sean.</li></ul>\n<p><strong>Resources:</strong></p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/products/site-selection-software\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">Sales Forecasting</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/products/site-selection-software\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">Zeus AI</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/schedule-a-demo\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">Proof of Concept</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/products/site-selection-software\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">White Space Analysis</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sitezeus.com/customer-stories\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">Customer Stories</a></li></ul>\n<p>Best,<br>lboney@sitezeus.com</p>",
